OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FAn attack on innocent children
OL,7,Fattending a dance class in Southport
OL,8,F'could and should' have been stopped
OL,9,Fif the killer's parents and state
OL,10,Fagencies had acted sooner, the inquiry
OL,11,Finto the atrocity has concluded.
OL,13,FIts chair, Sir Adrian Fulford, has
OL,14,Fmade 67 recommendations in a 700-page
OL,15,Freport into the attack by 17-year-old
OL,16,FAxel Rudakubana in July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
