FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FThe report, following a nine-week
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry at Liverpool Town Hall
OL,8,Fin 2025, focuses criticism on a number
OL,9,Fof state agencies along with the
OL,10,Fparents of the killer - referred to as
OL,11,F'AR' throughout the inquiry.
OL,13,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, Bebe
OL,14,FKing, six, and Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,15,Fseven, were murdered when AR entered
OL,16,Fthe Taylor Swift-themed dance workshop
OL,17,Fin The Hart Space, Southport, armed
OL,18,Fwith a knife.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FThe killer, then 17, also attempted to
OL,7,Fmurder eight other children, who
OL,8,Fcannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,9,Fclass instructor Leanne Lucas, and
OL,10,Fbusinessman John Hayes.
OL,12,FSir Adrian said his two "principal
OL,13,Fconclusions" were that AR's parents
OL,14,Fwere at fault in not reporting his
OL,15,Fescalating behaviour and state
OL,16,Fagencies including those in health,
OL,17,Feducation and policing, failed to
OL,18,Fmanage the risk the teenager clearly
OL,19,Frepresented.
OL,26,@tD@YOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FHad they done so, Sir Adrian said it
OL,7,Fwas "highly likely" the attack would
OL,8,Fnot have occurred.
OL,10,F"History simply would have taken a
OL,11,Fdifferent course," he said.
OL,13,F"As I have already indicated but I
OL,14,Frepeat, this terrible event could have
OL,15,Fbeen and should have been prevented.
OL,17,F"While the sole immediate cause of
OL,18,Fdeath was unlawful killing by the
OL,19,Fperpetrator, the attack that led to
OL,20,Fthe deaths was preventable."
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@SO]rD@AOUsD@RO]uD@AOUyD@AOU|D@
OL,26,A\O]
