OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FSir Adrian said there had been a
OL,7,F"repeated tendency" by multiple
OL,8,Fagencies to excuse the killer's
OL,9,Fbehaviour on the basis of his autism
OL,10,Fspectrum disorder.
OL,12,F"Agencies regularly used his autism as
OL,13,Fan explanation or even excuse for his
OL,14,Fconduct, including his violence," he
OL,15,Fsaid. "This was both unacceptable and
OL,16,Fsuperficial".
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FEven when it was recognised, Sir
OL,7,FAdrian noted, it was never properly
OL,8,Fidentified as a factor which
OL,9,F"significantly increased the risk he
OL,10,Fposed".
OL,12,FAll this, the chair said, meant the
OL,13,Funderlying risk was left "unmanaged".
OL,15,FSir Adrian also made it clear however,
OL,16,Fit would be "entirely wrong" to make a
OL,17,Fgeneral association between autism and
OL,18,Fan increased risk of violent harm to
OL,19,Fothers.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FThe teenage killer downloaded a wide-
OL,7,Frange of "vile and disturbing
OL,8,Fimagery", twice downloaded an academic
OL,9,Farticle that contained the text of an
OL,10,FAl-Qaeda training manual, as well as
OL,11,Farticles and papers relating to a
OL,12,Fvariety of conflicts and atrocities,
OL,13,Fthe inquiry heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FWhile there is no evidence AR's
OL,7,F"acutely inappropriate - and on
OL,8,Foccasion unlawful - online activity"
OL,9,Fwas known to any agency prior to the
OL,10,Fattack, there is, Sir Adrian said, a
OL,11,F"direct line" back to it from reports
OL,12,Fof the killer's earlier online
OL,13,Fbehaviour.
OL,15,FBut, this online behaviour - including
OL,16,Fseveral uses of school computers to
OL,17,Fmake inappropriate searches - was
OL,18,F"never properly appreciated by any
OL,19,Fagency or by AR's parents", Sir Adrian
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FIt formed the basis of three Prevent
OL,7,Freferrals by The Acorns School,
OL,8,FCounter Terrorism Police North West
OL,9,F(CTPNW) "did not deem AR vulnerable to
OL,10,Fbeing drawn into terrorism" and all
OL,11,Freferrals were closed.
OL,13,FThe lack of exploration of, or
OL,14,Fengagement with, AR's online life was
OL,15,F"a significant failing that hampered
OL,16,Fagencies from identifying and
OL,17,Faddressing the risk AR posed to others.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FSir Adrian added that in a digital age
OL,7,Fit should be self-evident that what
OL,8,Fsomeone searches online can be an
OL,9,F"effectively predictor for how they
OL,10,Fare likely to behave offline".
OL,12,FThese "obvious matters meant a crucial
OL,13,Fperspective on AR's thinking was never
OL,14,Fproperly explored despite the
OL,15,Fopportunities for that to occur", he
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FSir Adrian said AR's parents were
OL,19,Fready to "excuse and defend" their
OL,20,Fson's actions, and failed to "stand up
OL,21,Fto his behaviour and set boundaries".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FUltimately, he said, this led to their
OL,7,Ffailure to "do what they morally ought
OL,8,Fto have done" and report "the clear
OL,9,Fescalation of risk" in the week
OL,10,Fleading up to the attack.
OL,12,FIf they had, he said, "AR would not
OL,13,Fhave been at liberty to conduct the
OL,14,Fattack and it would not therefore have
OL,15,Foccurred".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FThe chair said while he recognised the
OL,7,Frole of AR's parents was "complex"
OL,8,Fthey - particularly his dad - "created
OL,9,Fsignificant obstructions to
OL,10,Fconstructive engagement with AR by the
OL,11,Fvarious agencies the were involved".
OL,13,FAs a consequence of the five failings
OL,14,FAR, who had "clearly revealed the
OL,15,Fextreme danger that he presented to
OL,16,Fothers as early as December 2019", was
OL,17,Fable to carry out the attack at the
OL,18,Fdance class in July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FSir Adrian said the incident, on 11
OL,7,FDecember 2019, where AR took knife
OL,8,Finto school wanting to kill pupil who
OL,9,Fhe perceived had bullied him before
OL,10,Fassaulting another pupil at random -
OL,11,Fwas "a watershed event".
OL,13,F"It put beyond doubt that AR was
OL,14,Fmotivated by an enduring desire to
OL,15,Finflict severe harm and possibly kill
OL,16,Fanother pupil... taken with the other
OL,17,Finformation available at the time,
OL,18,Fthis should have led all agencies
OL,19,Finvolved to a conclusion that AR posed
OL,20,Fa high risk of harm to others."
OL,26,@uD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
