FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776153957
OL,3,CWhat were the five key findings in the
OL,4,CSouthport report?
OL,6,FHe added: "It is significantly
OL,7,Ftroubling that no agency within our
OL,8,Fpublic services had the responsibility
OL,9,Fto monitor, investigate and take steps
OL,10,Fto neutralise a risk of this magnitude.
OL,12,F"Wholly separate from my view that the
OL,13,Fattack would not have occurred had
OL,14,FAR's parents reported what they knew
OL,15,Fin late July 2024, if appropriate
OL,16,Farrangements and reasonable resources
OL,17,Fhad been in place to address the risk
OL,18,Fthat AR posed to others from December
